Xpress Payment Solutions Limited has appointed Dr. Markie Idowu, as the new Managing Director/Chief Executive Officer of the organisation. According to a statement, Idowu was a former Executive Director, Technology and Service Delivery Channels at Polaris Bank Plc. He is a seasoned professional with over 31 years’ experience in Finance and Information and Communication Technology (ICT). According to the statement, “Idowu’s experience includes 28 years in banking spanning retail, commercial and corporate banking, treasury management, international business finance, operations, electronic banking and information technology. Idowu has served on the board of several companies including Skye Bank, MainOne Cable Company, Equity Assurance, IHS and Mainstreet brokers.”